reviewText: wow, what a lousy and poor bootleg! It's the Aquapalooza show from 2009, but there's 6 minutes missing and the DVD starts halfway through "Good Time". The CMT logo was replaced by a grey stamp that says "Alan Jackson" and it's displayed throughout the whole show. But most importantly, the quality of the video is so incredibly low. You can find a much better and full version of this show on Youtube.

This is pure bulls***!! Be aware! Do not buy this, this is not a documentary or have any interwievs or anything like that. This is only a concert at Appaloosa. Web is full of it. DVD has very poor picture and sound. No information with disc, no booklet no nothing :( I don't even know if the Laser Media exist.
I thought this DVD was going to include a documentary about Alan Jackson and it only contains 17 songs performed at the Aquapalooza concert from several years ago.
